OL,3,CMan who raped teenage girl jailed for
OL,4,C8 years
OL,6,FA man who raped and carried out other
OL,7,Fsexual offences on a teenage girl has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for eight years.
OL,10,FAaron Roberts, 33, of no fixed abode,
OL,11,Fcommitted the attacks in between May
OL,12,Fand September 2020.
OL,14,FHe was found guilty by the jury after
OL,15,Fa two-day trial in December 2023.
OL,17,FThe court heard that in May 2021 the
OL,18,Fvictim disclosed Roberts' crimes to
OL,19,Ftheir family and it was reported to
OL,20,Fthe police.
