OL,3,CMan who raped teenage girl jailed for
OL,4,C8 years
OL,6,FDuring the police investigation, it
OL,7,Fwas discovered that Roberts had sent
OL,8,Fthe victim inappropriate images of
OL,9,Fhimself via social media and forced
OL,10,Fher to commit sexual acts on him,
OL,11,Fbefore raping her.
OL,13,FOfficers recovered messages sent by
OL,14,FRoberts to the victim where he said
OL,15,Fthey 'have to do it again one day',
OL,16,Fwhich was said in relation to the
OL,17,Fsexual acts. He also suggested they
OL,18,Fshould delete the messages.
