OL,6,FWhen he was arrested and interviewed
OL,7,Fby officers in November 2021, Roberts
OL,8,Frepeatedly denied all of the
OL,9,Fallegations.
OL,11,FRoberts pleaded not guilty to the
OL,12,Foffences but after a short
OL,13,Fdeliberation, the jury found him
OL,14,Funanimously guilty of rape, inciting a
OL,15,Fchild to engage in sexual activity,
OL,16,Fsexual activity with a child,
OL,17,Fattempted rape and sexual
OL,18,Fcommunication with a child.
