OL,6,FRoberts appeared in the dock at Truro
OL,7,FCrown Court on 18 April where His
OL,8,FHonour Judge Robert Linford sentenced
OL,9,Fhim to eight years in prison. He will
OL,10,Falso sign the Sex Offenders' Register
OL,11,Ffor life.
OL,13,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,14,FConstable Distin said: "I would like
OL,15,Fto take this opportunity to commend
OL,16,Fthe victim for her bravery and immense
OL,17,Fcourage in coming forward to police to
OL,18,Freport this crime.
