OL,6,F"Nothing will take away the trauma
OL,7,Fthat she has been through, but we hope
OL,8,Fthat some reassurance can be offered
OL,9,Fin knowing that supporting a
OL,10,Fprosecution has brought this man to
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,F"We truly hope that this outcome gives
OL,14,Fother victims the strength to come
OL,15,Fforward and report incidents of rape
OL,16,Fand sexual assault to police and
OL,17,Freassures them that we have mechanisms
OL,18,Fin place to help support victims
