OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Andy Shortern
OL,8,Fsaid: "We welcome today's sentence, I
OL,9,Fwould like to thank the victim for
OL,10,Freporting to us and supporting the
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"This result would not have been
OL,14,Fpossible without the victim's courage.
OL,16,F"I would also like to praise
OL,17,FDetectives from the West Cornwall
OL,18,FPublic Protection Unit for their
OL,19,Ftenacity and commitment which has
OL,20,Fresulted in this dangerous offender
OL,21,Fbeing brought to justice."
